[Name] LibXFCE4UI
[Summary] Automatic management of removable drives and media for Thunar

[Description]
Thunar-volman is an extension for the Thunar File Manager, which enables automatic management of 
removable drives and media. For example, if Thunar-volman is installed and configured properly, 
and you plug in your digital camera, it will automatically spawn your preferred photo application 
and import the new pictures from your camera.

